  <!-- v1.0.4: ORIGINAL monochrome class emblems (hand-authored geometry, NOT sourced from Blizzard,
       Maxroll, Mobalytics, D4Builds, or any wiki — legally clean; see _design/MODERNIZATION_NOTES.md
       and _design/CLASS_ART_BRIEF.md). 64x64 space; #FFFFFF is a placeholder — the browse row tints
       each per class by using the emblem as an OpacityMask over a class-colored rectangle
       (NameToEmblemConverter). Inner detail = EvenOdd ("F0") holes so tinting stays a single color.
       Render-verified at 24/28/32/40px tinted-on-dark. x:Shared="False" for per-chip instances. -->

